OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man who was portrayed in a film as a 
OL,6, life-saving hero during the Rwandan    
OL,7, genocide has been sentenced to 25 years
OL,8, for terrorism by a court in Rwanda.    
OL,10,FPaul Rusesabagina, 67, was found guilty
OL,11,Fof backing a rebel group behind deadly 
OL,12,Fattacks in 2018 and 2019.              
OL,14,FHis family has called the trial a sham,
OL,15,Fsaying he was taken to Rwanda, from    
OL,16,Fexile, by force.                       
OL,18,FThe US, where Rusesabagina is a        
OL,19,Fresident, said it was concerned by the 
OL,20,Fconviction.                            
